text: Dieter Rauchbach (born 9 April 1934) is a German wrestler. He competed in the men's freestyle light heavyweight at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1934 births Category:Living people Category:German male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of the United Team of Germany Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Saxony-Anhalt
